Wheat 8 @ 5 each → 40 value  
Wood 20 @ 10 → 200

• Brick rises from 11→12, so I gain one Brick whose standalone price is 20; hence immediate value increase = 20.

Since we only report the offer when acting:

[Offer: 5 Wheat -> 1 Brick]
